{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"44af94f29d","title":"“大多数群众都是没有头脑的应声虫”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0a4f4495b5","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":29,"articleId":"44af94f29d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"b86e073e34","name":"西南师范学院"},{"id":"f58526bcf8","name":"董时光"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"88935058d6","type":"title","text":"“大多数群众都是没有头脑的应声虫”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"44af94f29d"},{"id":"7d22a5b525","type":"authors","text":"西南师范学院董时光","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"44af94f29d"},{"id":"106d868a3a","type":"paragraph","text":"西南师范学院讲师董时光在该院教师座谈会上说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"44af94f29d"},{"id":"67a90945e5","type":"paragraph","text":"群众有三种，根据我的分析，第一种最多，没有头脑，不能独立思考，只是跟着领导屁股后喊口号，不折不扣地作领导上的应声虫。第二种是极少数，他们喜欢拍马屁，无耻钻营，他们对领导什么肉麻的奉承话都说得出来。领导们也专门喜欢听这种人的话，往往诬良为奸，在每次运动中造成无数冤狱。第三种人是有良心有正义感，却不敢站起来说话。（摘自５月２９日重庆日报）","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"44af94f29d"},{"id":"bc3d3361d4","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：1957年6月15日《人民日报》第3版。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"44af94f29d"}],"page":{"id":"4a5b08a631","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"44af94f29d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}